             was indicted for <rs id="t18210411-59-off355" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210411-59-off355" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210411-59-off355" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18210411-59-cd356" type="crimeDate">10th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210411-59-off355 t18210411-59-cd356"></join>, one pistol, value 3 s.; one Bible, value 7 s.; one shawl, value 30 s.; one scarf, value 5 s.; four shirts, value 12 s.; five gowns, value 10 s.; four sheets, value 5 s.; one handkerchief, value 1 s.; two pair of stockings, value 6 s.; four petticoats, value 4 s., and one pestle and mortar, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18210411-59-victim630" type="victimName">
                        Richard 
                        Reeves
                     <interp inst="t18210411-59-victim630" type="surname" value="Reeves"></interp>
